desc: We specialize in sales of hard-to-find parts for John Deere Square Baler models 14T, 214T, 24T, 224T, 336, 346, 327, 337, 347, 328, 338, 348. We have a huge inventory of Tech-Certified used parts, new aftermarket parts and OEM parts. Also updated designs for Tucker Fingers, Slip Clutch Centers and Wiper Arm assemblies

layout.text: Quality parts and friendly advice for John Deere Small Square Baler Models 14T, 214T, 24T, 224T, 336, 346, 327, 337, 347, 328, 338, 348, some Wire and European Models
